      • pitchBend

        public static byte[] pitchBend(int ch,
                               double pitchBendValue)
        Specifying pitch bend value by a double-float numeric value. Range is ( -1 <= pitchBendValue <= 1 ) The resolution relies on only fourteen bits; thus any value change less than 0.0001 ( 1.0d/8192 â‰’ 0.0001 ) will not have any effect on the output value.
